data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and natural beauty in this charming 3-bedroom bi-level home.,From the tranquil oasis of mature trees, enclosed back yard with privacy fence and raised garden beds to the stunning mountain views that greet you each day, this home offers a unique living experience. With an automatic sprinkler system, you'll have lush greenery without the effort. Step inside to find laminate flooring that combines style with easy maintenance. The covered deck is a year-round outdoor haven, while elegant window blinds provide privacy and natural light control. Storage is a breeze with the 2-car garage, additional off-street parking, and a convenient shed for all your tools and equipment. Make this your forever home and enjoy the serenity of nature while living in complete comfort.   ***Sellers is offering to pay $4,000 toward buyers closing cost and prepaids at closing, with an acceptable offer.***
